{"tid":1761830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（學生網購丫叉）海關篤灰、差佬扮送貨、奶共法官唔準保釋","createTime":"2019-11-29T07:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T06:37:21.000Z","uid":202464,"like":23,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"431dd21382dc90b1004e3f39c1ae5ab577c2dc07","tid":1761830,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"1. 藍絲海關周二收到從美國寄來的包裹，懷疑內有可疑物品，交由警方處理；<br />\n<br />\n2. 警員假扮送貨員送件，並先後拘捕涉案大學生及其母親。<br />\n<br />\n3. 大學生最終被控企圖管有攻擊性武器罪，裁判官羅德泉拒絕被告的保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n4. 罪名：企圖管有攻擊性武器、即三副投射器以及六包彈珠，意圖用作非法用途。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登傳說：<br />\n<br />\n1.  海關有好多前線係黃<br />\n<br />\n2.  香港法治有險可守<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05c4035252f8fdb6a67c9ddffcf8a08d81627e6","tid":1761830,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44451017272e3f5532596abcbc3e26d284772bc7","tid":1761830,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:19:21.000Z","msg":"好正, 平行世界"},{"pid":"ddf79055ec71d4f6e2cb9706cbc0635c8640df02","tid":1761830,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/